cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.CR

The paper deals with iris recognition using deep learning-based image segmentation techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also extensively uses deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper deals with biometric authentication, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also discusses the use of irregular segmentation masks, which could be related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with security and privacy, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
